# Objective
Experimental VLE study for the water–ethanol system.

Workflow
Experimental measurements
→ Calibration
→ Composition estimation
→ NRTL regression
→ Aspen validation
→ Python implementation

Main Engineering Challenge
The original calibration curve did not cover ethanol-rich mixtures, requiring a literature-based recalibration.

Key Skills
• Experimental Thermodynamics
• Aspen Plus
• NRTL Regression
• Data Validation
• Python (ongoing)
